404	
405	Create this file. It is a self-contained React component for the Purge Unused workflow.
406	
407	**Behaviour:**
408	
409	- State: `phase: 'idle' | 'confirming' | 'done'` (default `'idle'`)
410	- `idle` phase: button "Purge Unused…" → sets phase to `'confirming'`
411	- `confirming` phase:
412	  - Show text: "This will remove unreferenced types, materials, and families (3 passes)."
413	  - Button "Confirm Purge" → calls `console.warn('purge-unused stub')` then sets phase to `'done'`
414	  - Button "Cancel" → sets phase to `'idle'`
415	- `done` phase: show text "Purge complete." and a "Close" button that resets phase to `'idle'`
416	
