465	Create `packages/web/src/collaboration/PurgeUnusedPanel.test.tsx` (vitest + @testing-library/react):
466	
467	1. **renders idle state** — render `<PurgeUnusedPanel />`; assert "Purge Unused…" button is in the document.
468	2. **transitions to confirming** — click "Purge Unused…"; assert "Confirm Purge" and "Cancel" buttons appear.
469	3. **cancel returns to idle** — click "Purge Unused…" then "Cancel"; assert "Purge Unused…" button is back.
470	4. **confirm purge** — spy on `console.warn`; click "Purge Unused…" then "Confirm Purge"; assert `console.warn` was called with `'purge-unused stub'` and "Purge complete." text appears.
